column3: I’m more concerned about them being in that water.

I bought these cargo bib shorts which are my first Rapha bibs and I have to say the crotch area is SUPER tight, i am not sure what's up, at first I thought I got the women's version by mistake. Is this kind of tight fit normal for Rapha bibs??
Useful but not short of £200 fuck me sideways
